{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857140147,"sessionID":"ses_286abd21bffeWpR8dmMKbZgVVY","part":{"id":"prt_d79555dfd001yxF0Ay1Vzhd3ih","messageID":"msg_d7954d0a1001YJTZxKf0pXtpjd","sessionID":"ses_286abd21bffeWpR8dmMKbZgVVY","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:14","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md","content":"# AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心 - Tasks\n\n## Open Tasks\n\n- [ ] Design proxy core architecture\n- [ ] Implement HTTP reverse proxy\n- [ ] Implement route table management\n- [ ] Implement header injection\n- [ ] Implement WebSocket support\n- [ ] Implement connection pooling\n- [ ] Implement timeout and circuit breaker\n- [ ] Implement metrics collection\n- [ ] Implement access logging\n- [ ] Write unit tests\n- [ ] Write integration tests\n\n## Completed Tasks\n\nNone yet.\n\n---\n\n*Last Updated: Draft*\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-008/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775857140128,"end":1775857140147}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857140149,"sessionID":"ses_286abd21bffeWpR8dmMKbZgVVY","part":{"id":"prt_d79557260001F4jSAvoIkRC30F","messageID":"msg_d7954d0a1001YJTZxKf0pXtpjd","sessionID":"ses_286abd21bffeWpR8dmMKbZgVVY","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:15","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-009/tests.md","content":"# AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心 - Test Specification\n\n## Test Plan\n\nTBD - Test plan will be defined during design phase.\n\n## Unit Tests\n\nTBD\n\n## Integration Tests\n\nTBD\n\n## Performance Tests\n\nTBD\n\n## Test Data\n\nTBD\n\n---\n\n*Status: Draft*\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-008/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-009/tests.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-009/tests.md","time":{"start":1775857140131,"end":1775857140148}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857140515,"sessionID":"ses_286abd21bffeWpR8dmMKbZgVVY","part":{"id":"prt_d7954dea1001UTaHarSEtH5xJg","messageID":"msg_d7954d0a1001YJTZxKf0pXtpjd","sessionID":"ses_286abd21bffeWpR8dmMKbZgVVY","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-009/spec.yaml","content":"id: AR-009\ntitle: Router HTTP 反向代理核心\nmodule: pkg/router\nlanguage: Go\nsize: M\nstatus: open\n\n# AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心\n# Module: pkg/router\n# Language: Go\n# Size: M\n\n# OpenSpec Metadata\nopenspec:\n  version: \"1.0\"\n  project: agentcube\n\n# Architecture Requirement\nrequirement:\n  type: reverse-proxy\n  description: |\n    Implement the core HTTP reverse proxy functionality for the agentcube router.\n    This component handles request routing from external clients to sandbox instances,\n    managing connection pooling, path rewriting, header manipulation, and load balancing.\n    It provides the primary ingress point for all sandbox-bound HTTP traffic.\n\n# Scope\nscope:\n  in:\n    - HTTP reverse proxy with request/response streaming\n    - Dynamic route table management for sandbox endpoints\n    - Path prefix stripping and rewriting\n    - Header injection (X-Sandbox-ID, authentication context)\n    - Connection pooling and keep-alive management\n    - Timeout and circuit breaker patterns\n    - WebSocket upgrade support\n    - Basic load balancing across sandbox replicas\n    - Request/response metrics collection\n    - Access logging for audit trail\n  out:\n    - TLS termination (handled by external ingress)\n    - Authentication/authorization (handled by auth middleware)\n    - Rate limiting (separate AR)\n    - Advanced load balancing algorithms (separate AR)\n    - Multi-region routing (separate AR)\n\n# Acceptance Criteria\nacceptance:\n  - HTTP requests are correctly routed to target sandbox instances\n  - Path prefix stripping works as configured\n  - Required headers are injected into proxied requests\n  - WebSocket connections are properly upgraded and proxied\n  - Connection pooling reduces overhead for repeated requests\n  - Timeouts prevent hung connections\n  - Circuit breaker prevents cascade failures\n  - Metrics exposed for request latency, throughput, errors\n  - Access logs capture essential request details\n  - Unit tests achieve >= 80% coverage\n  - Integration tests verify end-to-end proxy flow\n\n# References\nreferences:\n  - AR-008: Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n\n# Estimation\nestimation:\n  size: M\n  story_points: 5\n  days: 4\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-008/spec.yaml":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-009/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-009/spec.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-009/spec.yaml","time":{"start":1775857140113,"end":1775857140513}}}}
